body: "Verification plan:\n- Create a temporary directory outside the repository.\n- Initialize a fresh pm project and create at least one closed item.\n- Install pm-changelog from this checkout through pm install.\n- Run pm changelog generate from the extension.\n- Run the packed/linked standalone CLI against JSON input.\n- Confirm generated output contains the temporary closed item."
